    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its life. The exterior is clean with a strong shine, though you may find a few minor stone chips and light surface scratches consistent with careful regular use. Mechanically, it is very sound, starting reliably and shifting smoothly. The interior is in great shape, showing only light wear on the driver's seat bolster and common touchpoints. It\u2019s a dependable, attractive car that is ready for its next owner to drive home today without needing any immediate repairs.",
      "price": 33500.0,
