    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been consistently well-maintained by its previous owner. The engine runs strong with no mechanical issues, and the transmission shifts smoothly through all gears, making it a dependable option for daily commutes or long trips. The interior is clean and free of major tears, though you may find some minor cosmetic wear on the exterior consistent with its age. Overall, it is a solid, reliable car that is ready for the road without needing immediate repairs.",
      "price": 33500.0,
